'''Backstage Musikk A/S''' is a [[Norway|Norwegian]] chain of music stores.

They mainly sell guitars, basses and pianos. [[Fender Musical Instruments Corporation|Fender]], [[Gibson Guitar Corporation|Gibson]], [[Martin (guitars)|Martin]], [[Taylor Guitars|Taylor]], [[Yamaha]], [[Roland]], [[Korg]], [[Nord Electro]], [[Marshall Amplification|Marshall]] and [[Vox (musical equipment)|Vox]] are their main brands. The chain was established in 2009 in [[Sandvika]].<ref name=musikk>{{cite web|title=Backstage musikk|url=http://www.backstagemusikk.no/|publisher=backstagemusikk.no|accessdate=28 November 2013}}</ref><ref name=qesign>{{cite web|title=Backstage Musikk|url=http://www.qesign.com/offer.php?x=Backstage_Musikk_A/S|publisher=qesign.com|accessdate=28 November 2013}}</ref><ref name=hagstrom>{{cite web|title=Backstage Musikk|url=http://www.hagstromguitars.eu/index.php?option=com_zoo&task=item&item_id=515&Itemid=29|publisher=hagstromguitars.eu|accessdate=28 November 2013}}</ref>

