[[File:Casa Fernando Pessoa.jpg|thumb|300px|Casa Fernando Pessoa in [[Campo de Ourique]].]] '''Casa Fernando Pessoa''' is a [[cultural center]] in [[Campo de Ourique]] of [[Lisbon]], [[Portugal]].
==History== It was created in honor of the poet [[Fernando Pessoa]], and conceived as a "home of poetry". It is located in the building where Pessoa lived between 1920 and 1935.
The cultural center opened on November 30, 1993.
