The '''Concours Nationaux d'Entrée aux Cycles de Formation d'Ingénieurs''' is a national [[entrance examination]] for admission to [[Graduate school|graduate training]] for [[engineer]]s in [[Tunisia]]. Admission to [[engineering school]]s is based on these [[exam]]s.

Successful candidates are allowed to enroll at one of Tunisia's engineering schools. The exams are written and generally taken by students of [[Preparatory class|preparatory classes]] (classes préparatoires scientifiques et technologiques).<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cningenieur.rnu.tn |title=Concours : 2013 : Nationaux d'Entree aux Cycles d'Ingenieurs |publisher=Cningenieur.rnu.tn |accessdate=2013-10-21}}</ref>

